 <title>6 Award Winning Apps from AppJamming Summit 2018</title>
 <link>http://explore.appinventor.mit.edu/blogs/karen/2018/04/6</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden view-mode-rss view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/sites/explore.appinventor.mit.edu/files/sun.png&quot; style=&quot;float: left; margin-right: 10px; width: 15%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.firstcodeacademy.com/6-award-winning-apps-from-appjamming-summit-2018-71ef458940d4&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Read about the AppJamming Summit 2018&lt;/a&gt;, held in Hong Kong, and hosted by First Code Academy. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;This is a guest blog by MIT Master Trainer Michelle Sun.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/sites/explore.appinventor.mit.edu/files/blog/ap-jamming-summit.jpeg&quot; style=&quot;display:block; margin:auto; width: 100%; clear: both; padding-top: 20px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-blog-images field-type-image field-label-hidden view-mode-rss view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
